# 9. LDAP Integration Testing

Test Linux auth.

On APP01:

```
sssd
realmd
ldap-utils
```

Test:

```
ldapsearch
id testuser1
```

Goal:

Linux system authenticates against **Active Directory**.

---

# 10. Failure Testing (Important)

Simulate outages.

Examples:

Stop container

```
docker stop api
```

Stop AD

```
shutdown DC01
```

Break DNS.

Observe alerts in Grafana.

